source: With this enabled, selection will be cleared every time exposed filters are changed, select all will select all rows with exposed filters applied and view total count will take exposed filters into account. When disabled, select all selects all results in the view with empty exposed filters and one can change exposed filters while selecting rows without the selection being lost.
